snippet.title: Biped 2 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Biped 2 is coming soon on PC, PlayStation, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch with a cross-platform online COOP of up to 4 players. Check out the free DEMO on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3453220/Biped_2_Demo/
